{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"dfe949223f","title":"中央复江西省委关于搜查民主人士问题的意见","origin":"根据文件的原件打印","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"c4fdd57d58","index":0,"year":1955,"month":9,"day":29,"articleId":"dfe949223f"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-shzygz","name":"中国五十年代初中期的政治运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-shzygz":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"a66da94a45","type":"title","text":"中央复江西省委关于搜查民主人士问题的意见","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"dfe949223f"},{"id":"e1b3fc77d6","type":"appellation","text":"江西省委并告各省市委、自治区党委：","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"dfe949223f"},{"id":"496f082014","type":"paragraph","text":"你们九月十五日致中央十人小组两电均悉。","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"dfe949223f"},{"id":"17e2e0cebe","type":"paragraph","text":"（一）搜查人民代表和较高级民主人士，必须十分慎重。如果没有较充分的材料和把握，不要轻易搜查，免得使自己处于被动。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"dfe949223f"},{"id":"148c191088","type":"paragraph","text":"（二）你们所报要搜查的五个民主人士和人民代表，从所述材料看来，除个别嫌疑情节较大者外，其余均材料不足，情节不明。因此，对此五人暂时都不要进行搜查。熊、葛二人可由公安机关加强侦察工作，目前对他们的外围分子，倒可以抓紧一些搞，发现材料，为将来工作作准备。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"dfe949223f"},{"id":"efde669b61","type":"paragraph","text":"（三）搜查中央中营厂矿中的总、副工程师必须事先报中央批准。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"dfe949223f"},{"id":"e2d485346f","type":"paragraph","text":"各省市有同类问题，均应按上述原则办理。","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"dfe949223f"},{"id":"deea444a9e","type":"paragraph","text":" 中央一九五五年九月二十九日","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"dfe949223f"}],"page":{"id":"a1ecaf7647","publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"dfe949223f","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}